# Enterprise rider (placeholder): a single rider in a pod.
# Remap1 is the rider's shirt. Authored in pod 0 (radius 3.4 along +X in
# the wheel's X-Y plane); the rider ring rotates it about the axle (Z) with
# the wheel. The pods are enclosed, so the engine shows riders only at the
# bottom: 48 poses (3 sub-frames x 16 folded angles), single view.
# OBJ space: +X forward, +Y up, +Z right; origin at footprint-base centre.
